com.simiacryptus.mindseye.opt.orient

Class OwlQn

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.opt.orient.OwlQn
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OrientationStrategy<LineSearchCursor>

    public class OwlQn
extends Object
implements OrientationStrategy<LineSearchCursor>
    Orthant-Wise Limited-memory Quasi-Newton optimization This is a modified L-BFGS algorithm which uses orthant trust regions to bound the cursor path during the line search phase of each iteration
